title: Shrubbery Fields
description: This is my own Beatles out-takes, gotten a long time ago from another Pirate Bayer (Thanks!) It is from when they were working on the song: Strawberry Fields Forever. But I added some Videos of the finished song, gotten from Youtube,including pictures from Pablo Picasso! And if you are in the Bay Area (I'm not,) you can go and see Vinny Caggiano (look up the name on An' tell him you're buying a drink in honor of Tony M of The City! And buy him one too, before the show!
